    "en": {
      "title": "Russia bans Biden's wife-daughter ban",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Russian government has banned 25 other US senators, including the wife of US President Joe Biden and First Lady Jill Biden, and Biden's daughter, from visiting Russia.",
        "It is said that the Russian government has taken this decision as a one-off due to the sanctions and sanctions imposed on Russia by the United States.",
        "The United States has imposed sanctions on Russia over its military action against Ukraine."
      ],
